# How Clustering Works

Suppose we have customer information:

| Customer | Income | Spending Score |
| -------- | ------ | -------------- |
| A        | High   | High           |
| B        | High   | High           |
| C        | Low    | Low            |

The clustering algorithm groups:

Cluster 1

A, B

Cluster 2

C

